Flutter & Dart – The Complete Guide [2025 Edition] – Udemy
Instructor: Maximilian Schwarzmüller
Platform: Udemy
Duration: 40+ hours
Completion Year: 2025

Description:
Completed an in-depth course on Flutter and Dart focused on building cross-platform mobile applications for Android and iOS. Gained practical experience through hands-on projects, including a chat app with Firebase integration and a shopping list app with state management. Covered core Flutter concepts such as widgets, navigation, animations, REST APIs, Firebase, provider state management, and app deployment.

Key Skills Acquired:

Dart programming fundamentals

UI/UX design with Flutter widgets

Firebase authentication & cloud Firestore

State management with Provider

Asynchronous programming & HTTP

Responsive design for multiple screen sizes

App debugging and performance optimization
